     Enraged at learning Valdayana had stolen her medallion piece, the Feir`Dal ranger slammed out of her room and stormed to the Trade Commissioners' Office of Shadow Haven, scrawled two messages for delivery and ran towards the Luclin Nexus, reverting to wolf form en route.  As she approached the Antonican Scion, the wizard responsible for activating the portal that leads to the continent of Antonica on Norrath she heard a troll dressed in black plate mail inquiring how long until the portal would be reactivated.<br>
